# Div

we can also create our own boxes independent of the automatic boxes, to group together other items and boxes.
the way we can create these boxes is using
html element called
<div></div>
elements, and they are completely invisible and their work is to act as invisible boxes that creates and groups content in between it's tags.
it can be styles using the css. we can put as many elements as we want. the tags are called divs.

Div only acts as a container, and nothing else.
